# ProtectYourPC

1 - Turns on Express settings.

2 - Turns on Express settings.

3 - Turns off Express settings.

<OOBE>
   <ProtectYourPC>3</ProtectYourPC>
</OOBE>

# NetworkLocation

Home - Specifies a private home network.

Work - Specifies a private office network.

Other - Specifies neither a home or work network. Network discovery is disabled by default on this network type.

<OOBE>
   <NetworkLocation>Work</NetworkLocation>
</OOBE>